      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# 🎯 Omni-Channel Marketing Attribution\n\nWelcome to the **Marketing Attribution Dashboard**. This view provides a comparative analysis of how different models—from traditional heuristics to advanced game-theoretic approaches—distribute conversion credit across your marketing channels.\n\n**Models included**: First-Click, Last-Click, Linear, Markov Chains (Probabilistic), and Shapley Value (Game Theory)."
      }
